    "claim": "`redeemCollateral()` trusts `msg.sender == redemptionHandler` and immediately reduces `totalBorrow` plus transfers collateral using the handler-supplied `_amount`, but the pair never pulls, burns, or otherwise verifies that the corresponding debt tokens were actually retired.",
